==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[hardware]] [[store]]}}

# A [[merchant]] that [[sell]]s [[tools]] such as [[hammers]], [[saw]]s, [[wrenches]], etc., various [[fastener]]s such as [[nail]]s, [[screw]]s, [[nut]]s and [[bolt]]s, and similar [[object]]s known collectively as [[hardware]].  A hardware store will usually include a wide range of related [[sundry|sundries]] used in [[construction]] and [[repair]] such as [[lumber]], [[gardening]], [[plumbing]] supplies, [[carpet]]ing, [[paint]], [[appliances]], [[cleaning supplies]] and sundry items such as [[house number]]s.  Typically a hardware store carries virtually all of the types of tools, [[supply|supplies]] and [[equipment]] used to build [[objects]] (such as some [[furniture]] and [[fixtures]]) as well as construction of [[complete]] [[structure]]s such as [[house]]s and other [[building]]s.

